tch?v=uQuRk2K7QUU&amp;t=61s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuQuRk2K7QUU%26t%3D61s&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPYR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=f3d06b40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uQuRk2K7QUU&amp;t=61s</a>"},{"pid":"ff3ec69e2437705b931bd07f562d17196fecc090","tid":2310881,"uid":341313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a527d3e67b9e65251f710533e2b6f7c1034c4969","tid":2310881,"uid":60831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1e665ca4c5a4a6517c0ec43a38d52e47fe04cfa1","tid":2310881,"uid":134774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90bc0749a1bcaf18e97f70876c10bf83eb9eac69","tid":2310881,"uid":60831,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:48:11.000Z","msg":"有條片佢係台下面彈上舞台，擺個pose再慢慢徐副黑超，已經型到仆街<br />\n台下面啲人叫到傻晒，有啲暈埋要人抬出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:51:15.000Z","msg":"link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:58:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nBkNQZ-6QHg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnBkNQZ-6QHg&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPYR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=9a2d9edb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nBkNQZ-6QHg</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T23:38:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">// Super Bowl中場表演的長度，被嚴格限制在12分鐘內，大多數表演者都力圖塞進盡可能多的音樂。<br />\n<br />\nMichael Jackson是個例外。<br />\n<br />\n在Rose Bowl中央彈出來後，他完全靜止地站在那裏，注視全世界長達九十秒 &mdash; 九十秒。//</span><br />\n<br />\n早兩年訪問返呢場show嘅製作人Don Mischer，佢話當初同MJ傾好咗，應承俾MJ自己決定幾時開始表演<br />\n&hellip;點知條友真係企足成90秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為Super Bowl每秒都係天文價錢，跟住Don忍唔住，不停對住MJ個耳機大嗌叫MJ快手啲，但MJ除咗耳機，冇理到佢嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cunPhleWTXE\" data-sr-url=\"https:/